data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming tri-level residence boasts 4 bed & 2 baths, offering a perfect blend of comfort & style. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the contemporary elegance of luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring that spans throughout the entire home. One of the many highlights of the home is the custom wood accent wall in the front living room, adding a touch of rustic charm and making this space perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, adorned with butcher block countertops that add warmth and character to the space. Brand-new HVAC, the 3yr home warranty, already paid for and transferrable. Large detached garage serves as an ideal workshop space. Large fenced in backyard w/ above-ground pool. Your ideal lifestyle awaits in this Hampton gem!
